@startuml
!theme plain

participant "Streamlit UI" as UI
participant "RAG System" as RAG
participant "SageMaker Endpoint\n(LLM)" as LLM
participant "OpenSearch" as OS
participant "Embedding Model" as EM

UI -> RAG: User query
activate RAG

RAG -> EM: Generate query embedding
activate EM
EM --> RAG: Query embedding
deactivate EM

RAG -> OS: Retrieve relevant documents
activate OS
OS --> RAG: Retrieved documents
deactivate OS

RAG -> RAG: Construct prompt with retrieved info

RAG -> LLM: Send constructed prompt
activate LLM
LLM --> RAG: Generated response
deactivate LLM

RAG -> RAG: Process and format response

RAG --> UI: Display response to user
deactivate RAG

@enduml